### Key behaviors (verified)
- **True sliding window**: Every request prunes `timestamps.filter(ts => ts > now - windowMs)` before counting.
- Allow path sets `X-RateLimit-Limit`, `X-RateLimit-Remaining`, `X-RateLimit-Reset` (epoch seconds) and calls `next()`.
- Reject path returns 429 + exact JSON body + `Retry-After` header and does **not** call `next()`.
- Cleanup runs every 60s (unref'd) and removes IPs with no remaining active timestamps in the window.
- `limiter.close()` stops the timer so the process can exit cleanly.
- Full proxy note is included in the usage comments (covers `app.set('trust proxy', n)`).

